
Ranger Help for: guard
======================

SYNTAX:      guard/unguard
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE EXP:    NA
BASE SP:     variable

SUMMARY:    
This task teaches a follower to be your 'watchdog'. Once you command 
your follower to be on guard, it will attack anyone that enters the room!
Use this task with care. To make your follower be off guard, just type
unguard. This is an easy task, so any follower can learn it.

